Package org.bluezoo.gumdrop.servlet.jsp

Class ExpressionElement

java.lang.Object
org.bluezoo.gumdrop.servlet.jsp.ExpressionElement
All Implemented Interfaces:
JSPElement
public class ExpressionElement extends Object implements JSPElement
Represents a JSP expression element: <%= java expression %>.

Expressions contain Java expressions that are evaluated and their string representation is written to the output. The expression is automatically converted to a string and HTML-escaped if necessary.

Example expressions: 

 <%= new java.util.Date() %>
 <%= request.getParameter("username") %>
 <%= Math.random() * 100 %>

In the generated servlet, expressions are converted to: 

 out.print(expression);
Author:
Chris Burdess
